Package: seqcomp
Type: Package
Title: Sequential Comparison of Probabilistic Forecasts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Akbar", "Alasgarli",
    email = "alasgarliakbar@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements tools for sequential comparison of probabilistic
    forecasts, including binary and categorical scoring rules, anytime-valid
    confidence sequences, e-processes, Winkler-score comparisons, lag handling,
    and predictable-bound e-processes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/alasgarliakbar/seqcomp,
